with sparkly gloves
for the show.

10:28.192 --> 10:29.672
And, Ginzy, all those years
of stress

10:29.759 --> 10:31.631
raising four rowdy boys

10:31.718 --> 10:34.285
has given you
such a nervous mom-tummy

10:34.372 --> 10:36.592
that you make poots
all through this class.

10:36.679 --> 10:37.724
